  "monster": {
    "title": "Liris.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Liris has an armoured red body which hovers in mid-air and huge, compound eyes.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 161     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: +++      </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: +++      </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: ++++ +    </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: +..     </lightgrey><darkgrey>   rC: ...      </darkgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: +        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 130% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 42% to hit with the +6 short sword of the Dancing Scavenger and 16% to hit with your bite.\nIt has about 50% to hit you.\n\nAttack  Max Damage  \nHit     44          \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to steam and miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can fly.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nIt is currently targeting Aizul.\n\nThis monster has been temporarily summoned to this location. If angered it will immediately vanish, yielding no experience or items; it is incapable of using stairs.",
